title: Fire & Blood: Aegon III is Jon Snow
description:
Edited audio from the livestream on March 5th 2019. Aziz goes through the life of Aegon III, which is filled with an enormous number of parallels to Jon Snow. It can tell us a lot about what's coming for him...
